<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/7.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <title>YouTube2MP3 Pro - Free YouTube to MP3 Converter</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1> <i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i>   YouTube2MP3 Pro</h1>
        <form action="/convert-mp3" method="POST" id="form">
            <div class="inside-top-container">
            <p>Please insert a valid YouTube video URL</p>
            <input type="text" name="videoLink" id="link" placeholder="Enter YouTube video link" >
            <button id="convert-btn" type="submit"><i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i></i></button>
            </div>
            <div class="download-info <%= (typeof success != "undefined") ? "active" : "" %>">
    <% if(typeof success != "undefined" && success) { %>
        <div class="success">
            <h2>Conversion Successful!</h2>
            <p>Your file is ready to download...</p>
            <div class="song-info">
                <p><b><%= song_title %></b></p>
                <p id="size"><%= song_size%></p>
                <a href="<%= song_link %>" download>
                    <button id="download-btn" type="button">
                        <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-down"></i> DOWNLOAD
                    </button>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    <% } else if(typeof success != "undefined" && !success) { %> 
        <div class="error">
            <p><%= message %></p>
        </div>
    <% } %>
    </div>
</div>
</form>
</div>
<div class="container-2">
        <h1>YouTube2MP3 Pro</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome to <strong>YouTube2MP3 Pro</strong>, the easiest way to save your favorite YouTube content as MP3 or MP4 files.  
      Our tool is completely free, works online, and is optimized for both desktop and mobile users—no software installation required.
    </p>

    <h2>How it Works</h2>
      <p> 1. Find a video you want to convert on <a href="https://www.youtube.com" target="_blank">YouTube</a>. </p>
      <br>
      <p> 2. Copy the video link directly from your browser’s address bar or the YouTube app. </p>
      <br>
      <p> 3.Paste the link into the converter box and select whether you want MP3 (audio) or MP4 (video). </p>
      <br>
      <p> 4. Click the <strong>Convert</strong> button and wait a few seconds for processing. </p>
      <br>
      <p> 5. Download your converted file instantly and enjoy it offline—anytime, anywhere. </p>

    <h2>Why Choose YouTube2MP3 Pro?</h2>
    <p> 1. ✔ 100% Free and fast conversions. <br></p>
    <p> 2. ✔ Works on all devices and browsers. <br></p>
    <p> 3. ✔ No registration or software required. <br></p>
    <p> 4. ✔ High-quality audio and video downloads. <br></p>

    <p class="terms">
      By using <strong>YouTube2MP3 Pro</strong>, you agree to follow our Terms of Service.  
      Thank you for trusting us as your go-to YouTube to MP3 converter.
    </p>
</div>
</body>
</html>